---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Restaurant Marketing in Mississauga | Toronto Restaurant Growth"
  description="Mississauga restaurant marketing that gets you found on Google. We help restaurants along Hurontario, Dixie, and Streetsville grow their visibility and fill tables."
>
  <Navbar />

  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <nav style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #f5f5f0; font-size: 0.85rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Home</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      <a href="/locations/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Locations</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      Restaurant Marketing Mississauga
    </nav>

    <section style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 100px 24px 80px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Mississauga, Ontario</p>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Restaurant Marketing in Mississauga</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #ccc; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px;">
          Mississauga has one of the most diverse dining corridors in Canada — and one of the most underserved digital markets. The restaurants winning here are the ones showing up on Google first.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #E85D04; color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">The Local Food Scene</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Mississauga's Underrated Dining Scene</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          Mississauga rarely gets the dining press that Toronto proper does — but that's changing fast. Drive along Hurontario from the 401 south to Port Credit, or explore the Dixie-Dundas corridor, and you'll find a dining scene that rivals anything in the 416. Chinese, Indian, Caribbean, Ethiopian, Lebanese, Japanese — Mississauga's culinary diversity is staggering, and its population has the disposable income and frequency to support it.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          The challenge is visibility. Unlike downtown Toronto where foot traffic is a natural discovery channel, Mississauga is a driving market. Customers find restaurants through Google Maps before they ever leave the house. If you're not ranking in the top 3 for your cuisine and neighbourhood, you're effectively invisible to the exact customers you want.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          New development around Square One, City Centre, and Port Credit is bringing younger demographics with high dining frequency and strong social media habits. The restaurants positioned for digital visibility now will capture this growth as it compounds over the next five years.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">What We Do</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">What We Do For Mississauga Restaurants</h2>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin-top: 28px;">
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Google Maps Positioning:</strong> We optimize your GBP for the specific searches Mississauga customers make — from "halal restaurant Dixie" to "best sushi Square One" to "Ethiopian food Mississauga."</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Neighbourhood SEO:</strong> We target corridor-level searches — Hurontario, Port Credit, Streetsville, Clarkson — because Mississauga diners search by area, not just city.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Review Management:</strong> We build the systems that generate 5-star reviews consistently — because in a driving market where decisions are made at home, your rating is your first impression.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Social Media:</strong> Content built for Mississauga's multicultural dining community — platform-appropriate, neighbourhood-specific, and designed to reach your exact customer base.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Website Design:</strong> Fast, mobile-first restaurant websites that load before the customer changes their mind — essential in a market where they're deciding from the car.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Questions</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">How much does restaurant marketing cost in Mississauga?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Our Mississauga restaurant marketing packages start at $497/month for Google Maps and local SEO. Full-service packages run $997–$1,997/month. Every engagement starts with a free Google audit so you know exactly what's possible before committing.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 24px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #1a1a1a;">Do you serve all of Mississauga?</p>
          <p style="color: #444;">Yes — from Port Credit to Meadowvale, and every corridor in between. We also serve neighboring markets: <a href="/locations/brampton/" style="color: #E85D04;">Brampton</a>, <a href="/locations/etobicoke/" style="color: #E85D04;">Etobicoke</a>, and <a href="/locations/hamilton/" style="color: #E85D04;">Hamilton</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Also Serving</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 24px;">Restaurant Marketing Across the GTA</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/locations/scarborough/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Scarborough</a>
          <a href="/locations/brampton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Brampton</a>
          <a href="/locations/north-york/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">North York</a>
          <a href="/locations/etobicoke/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Etobicoke</a>
          <a href="/locations/vaughan/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Vaughan</a>
          <a href="/locations/markham/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Markham</a>
          <a href="/locations/hamilton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Hamilton</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #E85D04; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 28px;">
          Your Mississauga restaurant deserves to be found. Let's make it happen.
        </h2>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #E85D04; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
